<li id="lithub_daily_widget-9" class="widget widget_lithub_daily_widget"><div class="lithub-daily-header"><a href="/category/lit-hub-daily/"><b>Lithub</b> Daily</a></div><h2 class="widgettitle">February 19, 2024</h2>
<a href="https://lithub.com/lit-hub-daily-february-19-2024/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-233339 size-thumbnail" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Dave_McKean_-_Lucca_Comics__Games_2018_01-150x150.jpg" alt="Dave McKean" width="150" height="150" /></a>
<ul>
 	<li><a href="https://www.tcj.com/i-will-always-choose-reality-dave-mckean-retrospective/" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">Jake Zawlacki interviews Dave McKean</span></a></li>
 	<li><a href="https://reactormag.com/must-read-short-speculative-fiction-january-2024/" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">The latest in short speculative fiction</span></a></li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/books/2024/feb/16/novelist-kelly-link-i-was-drawn-to-the-monsters-and-half-naked-women-on-fantasy-covers" class="external" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: 400">An interview with Kelly Link</span></a></li>
</ul>
<a title="LitHub Daily: May 1, 2015" href="https://lithub.com/lit-hub-daily-february-19-2024/"><button>More News</button></a></li>
	    			</ul>
